OL,3,CStephen Lawrence's mother in disbelief
OL,4,Cat claim police sought to 'smear'
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,FThe mother of Stephen Lawrence has
OL,8,Fspoken of her disbelief at claims that
OL,9,Fundercover officers were tasked with
OL,10,Ffinding information to "smear" and
OL,11,F"destroy" her family.
OL,13,FBaroness Doreen Lawrence told the
OL,14,Fpublic inquiry into undercover
OL,15,Fpolicing on Thursday she had only
OL,16,Fwanted to be treated the same as any
OL,17,Fother family by police.
