OL,3,CStephen Lawrence's mother in disbelief
OL,4,Cat claim police sought to 'smear'
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,FHer son Stephen was murdered by a
OL,8,Fracist gang of five or six attackers
OL,9,Fin south-east London in April 1993,
OL,10,Fonly two of whom have been ever been
OL,11,Fbrought to justice.
OL,13,FIncompetence and claims of corruption
OL,14,Fdogged the first failed investigation
OL,15,Finto his death, and in 2014 whistle-
OL,16,Fblower and former undercover officer
OL,17,FPeter Francis claimed he had been
OL,18,Ftasked with gathering information to
OL,19,Fsmear the Lawrence family.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
