OL,3,CStephen Lawrence's mother in disbelief
OL,4,Cat claim police sought to 'smear'
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,FThis is denied by the Metropolitan
OL,8,FPolice.
OL,10,FLady Lawrence said: "If they were able
OL,11,Fto put that amount of attention and
OL,12,Fresources into discrediting us as a
OL,13,Ffamily, if they'd put that amount of
OL,14,Fattention into seeking and to finding
OL,15,FStephen's murderers, we would not be
OL,16,Fsitting here today.
OL,18,F"All the time during Stephen's
OL,19,Finvestigation all I wanted was to be
OL,20,Ftreated the same. I wasn't looking for
OL,21,Fspecial treatment.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/12
