OL,3,CStephen Lawrence's mother in disbelief
OL,4,Cat claim police sought to 'smear'
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,F"It is your job to investigate
OL,8,FStephen's murder and that's all I
OL,9,Fwanted.
OL,11,F"To have spent their time looking to
OL,12,Fsmear and to find things to destroy us
OL,13,Fas a family, it's hard to believe that
OL,14,Fpeople go to that extreme."
OL,16,FShe told the hearing that police
OL,17,Fassumed her family were criminals
OL,18,Fbecause they were black.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/12
