OL,7,F"Police officers were saying that
OL,8,Fthey'd never met anybody like us
OL,9,Fbefore.
OL,11,F"And the assumption is that my son
OL,12,Fmust have been a criminal, and that
OL,13,Fwas what they kept bringing up.
OL,14,FBecause we were supposed to be so
OL,15,Fdifferent."
