OL,7,FLady Lawrence went on: "That was quite
OL,8,Fdisturbing, because automatically you
OL,9,Fare put into a category that as blacks
OL,10,Fyou are criminals, and there is
OL,11,Fnothing about me, my background,
OL,12,Fanything could ever give you that
OL,13,Fimpression."
