OL,7,FShe said the police did not seem
OL,8,Finterested in investigating her son's
OL,9,Fmurder and did not act on information
OL,10,Fpassed on by them and people in the
OL,11,Flocal community.
OL,13,FLady Lawrence told the hearing: "If
OL,14,FStephen had been white they would have
OL,15,Flooked at it completely differently."
OL,17,FMembers of the public passed on names
OL,18,Fof suspects, which the Lawrences gave
OL,19,Fto the police, but no effective action
OL,20,Fwas taken.
