OL,3,CStephen Lawrence's mother in disbelief
OL,4,Cat claim police sought to 'smear'
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,F"The police did not want to know.
OL,8,FPeople in authority did not want to
OL,9,Fknow. Just another black boy has been
OL,10,Fmurdered, so what? We were ignored.
OL,11,FConstantly ignored," she said.
OL,13,FLady Lawrence added: "We had done
OL,14,Feverything that we could do to support
OL,15,Fthe police, but in the end they did
OL,16,Fnothing to support us."
OL,18,FShe was shown a series of intelligence
OL,19,Freports that made reference to the
OL,20,Ffamily's justice campaign.
