OL,7,FSome suggested that political groups
OL,8,Fwanted to influence the campaign while
OL,9,Fothers were linked to plans for
OL,10,Fprotests during the Macpherson Inquiry
OL,11,Finto Stephen's death in 1998.
OL,13,FOutrage over the claims that Stephen
OL,14,FLawrence's family had been spied on
OL,15,Fwas one of the key catalysts for the
OL,16,Fmammoth Undercover Policing Inquiry,
OL,17,Fwhich began in 2015.
