OL,7,FWhistleblower Mr Francis said that his
OL,8,Fbosses were racist, with one known as
OL,9,FHN86 referring to black justice
OL,10,Fcampaigners as monkeys, which the
OL,11,Fofficer denies.
OL,13,FMr Francis has also claimed: "The
OL,14,FSpecial Branch attitude towards the
OL,15,FLawrence family was 100% racist.
OL,17,F"They were viewed as unable to think
OL,18,Ffor themselves or come up with and run
OL,19,Ftheir campaign themselves."
