OL,7,FThe UCPI is looking at the activities
OL,8,Fof undercover officers from the
OL,9,Fsecretive Metropolitan Police units
OL,10,Fthe Special Demonstration Squad (SDS)
OL,11,Fand the National Public Order
OL,12,FIntelligence Unit.
OL,14,FIt is claimed that they deceived women
OL,15,Finto sexual relationships, including
OL,16,Fhaving children, used the identities
OL,17,Fof deceased children without their
OL,18,Ffamilies' permission, and spied on
OL,19,Ffamily justice campaigns.
